        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Death Tax Repeal Act of 201</strong>7</p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) repeal the estate and generation-skipping transfer taxes, and (2) make permanent the maximum 35% gift tax rate and the lifetime gift tax exemption. The bill also provides for an inflation adjustment to such exemption amount.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
